text: Nameless Men is a 1928 American silent drama film directed by Christy Cabanne and starring Claire Windsor, Antonio Moreno and Eddie Gribbon.Monaco p.91 ==Cast== * Claire Windsor as Mary * Antonio Moreno as Robert Strong * Eddie Gribbon as Blackie * Ray Hallor as Hughie * Charles Clary as Mac * Carolynne Snowden as Maid * Sally Rand * Stepin Fetchit ==References== ==Bibliography== * Monaco, James.
